Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.18,0:01:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still wanna dance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.24,0:01:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, one day my passion's fire will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,From the beginning I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.83,0:01:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,One day the flames would die out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.54,0:01:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I thought I didn't need anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.46,0:01:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But even now, I'm so serious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.59,0:01:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... but I'm gonna burn it up, baby
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.64,0:01:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling, it's not that easy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.60,0:01:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But surely it's not that bad either
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it up, baby.  \N I'm gonna burn it up, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling Hurry up  \N Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling Hurry up  \N Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.13,0:02:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.01,0:02:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it up, baby.  \N I'm gonna burn it up, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,#4 The story of the cursed sword
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:03:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't hear a word you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's deaf up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Been standing there for half an hour now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's as wet as a drowned rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He can catch a cold for all I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain. \NI think he's listening to the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I told you, he can't hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from a rich family, aren't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty words and a ladylike face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not some country girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The past is the past. \NI'm just another peddler now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what were you praying \Nso hard about just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Good business?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I was praying that my brother \Nwould come home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To fight a war. It's been 5 years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,5 years? If it's been that long, \Nhe's probably already...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Help... me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you run off like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How could anyone do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, why the hell did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This sword was thirsty for blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I killed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A thirsty sword? Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no ordinary sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alive, a cursed sword \Nthat drinks human blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you have it in your hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,it controls your body \Nto kill anyone alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're blaming that sword \Nfor all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That smirk on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You are like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a demon in that blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not as quick as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He fell from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he's... Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your leg, huh. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is. That sword, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so creepy. I'm throwing it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad, you've come to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Osushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is I.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I prayed so hard for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That you would come home safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So having you here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll come back to me anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it, I don't want to go that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You stupid sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Whacha doin there, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Head on back to town. \NThere's danger in these woods...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the phantom killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.65,0:09:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Osushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To fight is a samurai's duty.  \N Please understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Father and Mother will look over us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be gone long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They were selling this out on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Chestnut rice. \NYou've always liked it, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember how when I was a child, \NI'd never stop crying once I got started?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much Mother tried, \NI'd keep crying and crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And when that happened, you'd come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And fold a paper crane.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd stop crying just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd sit there and gaze at the crane.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here! The phantom killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, let us go home. \NCome home with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What made you like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him. Kill him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Slice his head off, Tanosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He has built quite a magnificent castle  \N for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a great army  \N could conquer it easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he double crosses us, \Nhe could expose its weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be less secure than a sandcastle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We must kill him before that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please reconsider, my lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you disobey me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then take your own life with this sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an old sword  \N that had been stored away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rusty and dull.  \N Just right for you, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now kill him. Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That sword is said to become sharper  \N as it soaks in more blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's only a rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:15:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's enough blood here to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nihiru. That is your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It wants more blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nihiru says so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want more blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:15:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,As much as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Osushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You dummy, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, can't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.14,0:16:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me, Osushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let go. \N-Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:17:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't defend the house \Nnor the land on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But with you here with me, \Nwe could live again like before...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.32,0:17:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care \Nif you're not the same anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nihiru is calling for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This sword is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine and only mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you let me live?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.42,0:18:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have killed me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,before I got Nihiru back in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We searched everywhere, \Nbut couldn't find the midwife.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.47,0:21:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing about the baby, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.47,0:22:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorrow scatters in the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.18,0:22:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,piling up to form shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.22,0:22:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Our footsteps admonish \Nindifference in such verbose ways
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,As I peek into your fathomless eyes, \NI lose my composure
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.28,0:22:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any hope \Nin the place I am heading to?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.20,0:22:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I feign amusement and laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.45,0:22:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,because this road is so dark
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.79,0:23:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be there to shine the light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.67,0:23:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to playing at saying goodbye,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.88,0:23:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but I cried when I waved to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.10,0:23:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Our fiery woes fade... and fade...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.39,0:23:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,until night falls upon us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.52,0:23:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If I knew tomorrow would be so mundane,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.90,0:23:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have said that I wanted to live
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.15,0:23:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's futile but can't help dreaming \Nof a future... a future... you are to blame
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.14,0:23:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nihiru"
